00:38:58,664 --> 00:39:00,719
I just don't like him.

446
00:39:01,646 --> 00:39:04,461
Should we go to Hua Hin this weekend?

447
00:39:05,339 --> 00:39:09,430
Prince, I want to thank you a million times for bringing back the old Fah.

448
00:39:09,430 --> 00:39:11,290
I love you.

